org.hibernate.reactive.loader

Interface CachingReactiveLoader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ReactiveLoader

    public interface CachingReactiveLoader
extends ReactiveLoader
    Defines common reactive operations inherited by query loaders, in particular, interaction with the cache.
